**Location**: `/packages/provider-utils/src/convert-image-model-file-to-data-uri.ts`

Utility for converting ImageModelV3File to data URIs:
```typescript
function convertImageModelFileToDataUri(file: ImageModelV3File): string {
  if (file.type === 'url') return file.url;
  return `data:${file.mediaType};base64,${
    typeof file.data === 'string'
      ? file.data
      : convertUint8ArrayToBase64(file.data)
  }`;
}
```

