# Plan: Add PixelArt Provider Package to Vercel AI SDK

## Context

The Vercel AI SDK is a monorepo supporting many AI providers via a consistent adapter pattern. A new fictional "PixelArt" provider needs to be added that **only** supports image generation. This plan follows the exact same conventions as other providers (especially `packages/togetherai` as the closest simple reference) to ensure the package compiles cleanly and integrates properly.

---

## Files to Create

All files live under `packages/pixelart/`. No existing files are modified (except noting root `tsconfig.json` would need `{ "path": "packages/pixelart" }` added for full monorepo type-checking, but `pnpm type-check` from within the package works without it).

---

## Step-by-Step Implementation

